    "title": "Mafanikio ya Kweli",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "mafanikio ya kweli",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Mungu anataka watu wake wajitolee kikamilifu kwake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:4-Deut6:6\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 6:4–6</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:37\">Mathayo 22:37</a>). Mafanikio ya kweli yanatokana na kumtafuta Mungu na kumtambua kama mtawala, huku wakiepuka miungu yote ya uongo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:33\">Mathayo 6:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:21\">1 Yohana 5:21</a>). Kwa watu wa Israeli, mafanikio yalitegemea utiifu wao kwa agano la Mungu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:1-Lev26:46\">Mambo ya Walawi 26:1–46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:1-Deut28:68\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 28:1–68</a>). Hali ya kiroho ya Israeli na viongozi wake iliathiri sana kama wangeendelea kuwa na kibali cha Mungu na kubaki katika nchi ya ahadi.</p><p>Mwandishi wa 1–2 Wafalme huanza hadithi ya kila mtawala kwa kutoa tathmini ya kiroho. Mara nyingi, hii inalinganisha ibada ya kila mfalme kwa Mungu na mfano wa Mfalme Daudi (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:38\">1 Wafalme 11:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:8\">14:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:3-1Kgs15:5\">15:3–5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:11\">11</a>). Vitabu hivi vinaonyesha kuwa mustakabali wa Israeli na Yuda unategemea uongozi wa kiroho wa wafalme wao. Watu wa Mungu wangeweza kufanikiwa tu Kanaani ikiwa wangeabudu Mungu kwa uaminifu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:4-Deut12:7\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 12:4–7</a>). Maandishi mara nyingi yanakosoa ibada ya miungu ya uongo katika maeneo ya ndani (tazama, kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:2-1Kgs3:4\">3:2–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:7\">11:7</a>).</p><p>Kuanzia na Mfalme Yeroboamu I, wafalme wa Israeli (ufalme wa kaskazini) walijihusisha na ibada ya uongo, na Maandiko yanawakosoa kwa hilo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:31-1Kgs12:32\">1 Wafalme 12:31–32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:33-1Kgs13:34\">13:33–34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:25-1Kgs15:26\">15:25–26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:33-1Kgs15:34\">33–34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:11-1Kgs16:13\">16:11–13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:25-1Kgs16:26\">25–26</a>). Miongoni mwa wafalme hawa, Mfalme Ahabu alikuwa mwovu zaidi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:30-1Kgs16:33\">16:30–33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:25-1Kgs21:26\">21:25–26</a>). Mwanawe Ahazia alifuata mfano wake, na Mungu alimlaani kwa ibada yake ya miungu ya uongo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:51-1Kgs22:53\">22:51–53</a>).</p><p>Wafalme wa ufalme wa kaskazini waliwaongoza watu wao kuelekea uhamisho usioepukika (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:21-2Kgs17:23\">2 Wafalme 17:21–23</a>). Licha ya majaribio ya mara kwa mara ya Mungu ya kupata usikivu wao, hawakusikiliza (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:13-2Kgs17:15\">2 Wafalme 17:13–15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:23\">23</a>). Hivyo, Mungu aliwapa matokeo ya kutokuwa waaminifu kiroho kwa kuendelea (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:33-1Kgs13:34\">1 Wafalme 13:33–34</a>).</p><p>Wafalme wengine wa Yuda (ufalme wa kusini) wanapokea sifa, lakini Maandiko yanawakosoa wengi wao. Rehoboamu aliruhusu ibada ya miungu ya uongo kuenea Yuda (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:22-1Kgs14:24\">1 Wafalme 14:22–24</a>). Abiya aliendeleza dhambi za baba yake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:3\">15:3</a>). Maandiko hata yanawakosoa wafalme wazuri Asa na Yehoshafati kwa kuruhusu maeneo maarufu ya ibada za kienyeji kubaki (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:14\">15:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:43\">22:43</a>). Kushindwa kumpa Mungu nafasi yake halali kulisababisha matokeo mabaya.</p><p>Wafalme na watu wa ufalme wa kaskazini walionekana kuwa wapumbavu kwa kufanya walivyotaka. Hata hivyo, Bwana atabariki na kutoa furaha ya kweli kwa wale wanaoheshimu na kuishi kwa amri zake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:12\">Zaburi 33:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:1-Ps119:2\">119:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:15\">144:15</a>). Mafanikio ya kweli yanatokana na kumtambua na kumtumaini Mungu kama mtawala wa maisha ya mtu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:33\">Mathayo 6:33</a>). Kama ilivyoonyeshwa na Yesu na wafuasi wake wa mwanzo, mafanikio hayamaanishi kila mara kuwa na utajiri wa mali. Furaha na amani hutokana na kuishi kwa mapenzi ya Mungu na kumtumaini yeye (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:8-Phil3:14\">Wafilipi 3:8–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12-1Pet4:19\">1 Petro 4:12–19</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:1-Deut6:8\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 6:1–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:4-Deut12:7\">12:4–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:7-Josh1:8\">Yoshua 1:7–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:14\">1 Samweli 18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:38\">1 Wafalme 11:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:26-1Kgs12:33\">12:26–33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:1-1Kgs13:3\">13:1–3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:33-1Kgs13:34\">33–34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:8-1Kgs14:11\">14:8–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:13-2Kgs17:23\">2 Wafalme 17:13–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:12\">Zaburi 33:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:1-Ps119:2\">119:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:15\">144:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:33\">Mathayo 6:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:25-Luke10:28\">Luka 10:25–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:21\">1 Yohana 5:21</a></p>",
